                "invention-title": [
                    "Oxygen-free dehydrogenation helium recovery process",
                    "无氧脱氢的氦气回收工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "According to the oxygen-free dehydrogenation helium recovery process, oxygen-free dehydrogenation helium recovery equipment is adopted, a crude helium separation unit is communicated with a crude helium dehydrogenation unit through a hydrogen-rich crude helium pipeline, and the crude helium dehydrogenation unit is communicated with a solvent regeneration unit through a dehydrogenation organic solvent pipeline and a hydrogen-loaded organic solvent pipeline; the crude helium dehydrogenation unit is communicated with a low-temperature adsorption unit through a trace hydrogen crude helium pipeline, and the method comprises the following steps: 1, carrying out crude helium extraction on non-condensable gas by adopting a crude helium separation unit to obtain hydrogen-rich crude helium; 2, carrying out dehydrogenation treatment on the hydrogen-rich crude helium gas by adopting a crude helium dehydrogenation unit, and removing a hydrogen component to the ppm-level content, so as to obtain trace hydrogen crude helium gas; and 3, further purifying the trace hydrogen crude helium gas by adopting a low-temperature adsorption unit to obtain high-purity helium gas, and directly discharging the high-purity helium gas into the atmosphere. The oxygen-free dehydrogenation helium recovery process provided by the invention solves the problem that in the prior art, dehydrogenation is carried out by adding oxygen or air, and danger is easy to occur in the reaction process."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了无氧脱氢的氦气回收工艺，采用一种无氧脱氢氦气回收设备，粗氦分离单元通过富氢粗氦气管道连通有粗氦脱氢单元，粗氦脱氢单元通过脱氢有机溶剂管道和载氢有机溶剂管道连通有溶剂再生单元，粗氦脱氢单元通过痕氢粗氦气管道连通有低温吸附单元，步骤如下：1：采用粗氦分离单元对不凝气进行粗氦气提取，得富氢粗氦气；2：采用粗氦脱氢单元对富氢粗氦气进行脱氢处理，将氢组分脱除至ppm级含量，得到痕氢粗氦气；3：采用低温吸附单元对痕氢粗氦气进行进一步提纯，得到高纯氦气，直接排放至大气即可。本发明提供的无氧脱氢的氦气回收工艺，解决了现有技术通过加氧气或者加空气进行脱氢，此反应过程中容易发生危险的问题。"
                }
            ]
